{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"ty97p2rgy2xtu104b2kiwqf","title":"Signing Commit","desc":"","updated":1662143359203,"created":1662141421220,"custom":{},"fname":"software.git.signing-commit","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"57ba696b78396ad1c86bf3d82e991d2e","links":[{"type":"ref","from":{"fname":"software.git.signing-commit","id":"ty97p2rgy2xtu104b2kiwqf","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"linux.command.export-gpg","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":309},"end":{"line":11,"column":37,"offset":345},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"linux.command.export-gpg","anchorHeader":"import"}}],"anchors":{"use-gpg-key-to-sign-commit":{"type":"header","text":"Use gpg key to sign commit","value":"use-gpg-key-to-sign-commit","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"genrate-gpg-key":{"type":"header","text":"Genrate GPG key","value":"genrate-gpg-key","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"import-exsiting-gpg-key":{"type":"header","text":"Import exsiting gpg key","value":"import-exsiting-gpg-key","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"set-up-git-gpg-key":{"type":"header","text":"Set up git gpg key","value":"set-up-git-gpg-key","line":19,"column":0,"depth":2},"set-up-vs-code":{"type":"header","text":"Set up VS Code","value":"set-up-vs-code","line":55,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"yg542aqfl2wvgdfyhkanzzg","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"signing-commit\">Signing Commit<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#signing-commit\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"use-gpg-key-to-sign-commit\">Use gpg key to sign commit<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#use-gpg-key-to-sign-commit\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/about-commit-signature-verification\">https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/about-commit-signature-verification</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"genrate-gpg-key\"><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/generating-a-new-gpg-key\">Genrate GPG key</a><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#genrate-gpg-key\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"import-exsiting-gpg-key\">Import exsiting gpg key<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#import-exsiting-gpg-key\"></a></h2>\n<p></p><p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">Export Gpg</span></div>\n<a href=\"/notes/2gi29jkx904kfzav2vav9ab\" class=\"portal-arrow\">Go to text <span class=\"right-arrow\">→</span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"portal-parent-anchor\" class=\"portal-parent\" markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-top\"></div>\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-bottom\"></div><h2 id=\"import\">Import<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#import\"></a></h2>\n<p><code>gpg --import &#x3C;private key file location>.key</code></p>\n</div></div><p></p><p></p>\n<h2 id=\"set-up-git-gpg-key\">Set up git gpg key<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#set-up-git-gpg-key\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Show current gpg keys</p>\n<pre><code>gpg --list-secret-keys --keyid-format=long\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>add gpg key to Github</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Settings</li>\n<li>Access</li>\n<li>SSH &#x26; GPG keys</li>\n<li>New GPG key</li>\n<li>Paste the key</li>\n<li>Add GPG Key</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add gpg key to Git</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>list existing key</p>\n<pre><code>$ gpg --list-secret-keys --keyid-format=long\n\n### EXAMPLE RESPONSE\n/Users/hubot/.gnupg/secring.gpg\n------------------------------------\nsec   4096R/&#x3C;em>3AA5C34371567BD2&#x3C;/em> 2016-03-10 [expires: 2017-03-10]\nuid                          Hubot &#x3C;hubot@example.com>\nssb   4096R/42B317FD4BA89E7A 2016-03-10\n</code></pre>\n<p>=> key id: <strong>3AA5C34371567BD2</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add to Git</p>\n<pre><code>git config --global user.signingkey &#x3C;key id>\ngit config --global commit.gpgsign true\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add to <code>.bashrc</code> for startup setting</p>\n<pre><code>$ [ -f ~/.bashrc ] &#x26;&#x26; echo 'export GPG_TTY=$(tty)' >> ~/.bashrc\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"set-up-vs-code\">Set up VS Code<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#set-up-vs-code\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Enable auto signing\n<pre><code># settings.json\n\"git.enableCommitSigning\": true\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](h